bpftrace: bpftrace (a high-level tracing utility for eBPF)
bpftrace:
bpftrace: bpftrace is a high-level tracing language for Linux. bpftrace uses
bpftrace: LLVM as a backend to compile scripts to eBPF-bytecode and makes use
bpftrace: of libbpf and bcc for interacting with the Linux BPF subsystem, as
bpftrace: well as existing Linux tracing capabilities.
bpftrace: The bpftrace language is inspired by awk, C, and predecessor tracers
bpftrace: such as DTrace and SystemTap.
